## Conversiones Vite в†’ Next.js

| Vite (Figma V1.1) | Next.js (ProducciГіn) |
|---|---|
| Sin directiva | Agregar `"use client"` si usa hooks/state/events |
| `import { useNavigate } from 'react-router'` | `import { useRouter } from 'next/navigation'` |
| `navigate('/path')` | `router.push('/path')` |
| `useLocation()` de react-router | `usePathname()` de next/navigation |
| `<a href="/path">` internas | `<Link href="/path">` de next/link |
| `import xxx from 'figma:asset/...'` | Mover asset a `/public/images/` y usar `/images/...` |
| `import { useTheme } from '../context/ThemeContext'` | `import { useTheme } from '@/contexts/ThemeContext'` |
| `import { useFeatureToggle } from '../context/FeatureToggleContext'` | `import { useFeatureToggle } from '@/contexts/FeatureToggleContext'` |

## Comandos

```bash
cd ~/Documents/davidsons-design
npx tsc --noEmit    # ValidaciГіn TypeScript
npm run build       # Build completo
npm run dev         # Dev server
```
